{
 "fragments": [
  {
   "begin": "0.000", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "4.360", 
   "id": "s000001", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Herr Pr\u00e4sident! "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "4.360", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "8.840", 
   "id": "s000002", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Werte Kolleginnen und Kollegen! "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "8.840", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "10.680", 
   "id": "s000003", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Herr Kollege Klein, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "10.680", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "11.920", 
   "id": "s000004", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "es ist sicher richtig: "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "11.920", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "15.440", 
   "id": "s000005", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Die Bundesrepublik Deutschland tut viel in diesem Bereich. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "15.440", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "17.120", 
   "id": "s000006", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Die Frage ist aber, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "17.120", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "19.720", 
   "id": "s000007", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "ob wir nicht noch mehr tun k\u00f6nnen."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "19.720", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "22.040", 
   "id": "s000008", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Ich will es ganz deutlich sagen, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "22.040", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "24.640", 
   "id": "s000009", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Herr Kekeritz: "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "24.640", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "28.200", 
   "id": "s000010", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Der Antrag der Gr\u00fcnen hat meine volle Sympathie;"
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "28.200", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "34.240", 
   "id": "s000011", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "denn die Unterst\u00fctzung der Globalen Entwicklungspartnerschaft ist nicht nur sinnvoll, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "34.240", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "36.360", 
   "id": "s000012", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "sondern auch dringend notwendig. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "36.360", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "37.760", 
   "id": "s000013", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Wir wissen, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "37.760", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "42.480", 
   "id": "s000014", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "dass die Globale Entwicklungspartnerschaft ein besonderes Instrument ist, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "42.480", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "43.960", 
   "id": "s000015", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "weil es nicht nur darum geht, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "43.960", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "45.960", 
   "id": "s000016", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "unmittelbar Geld zur Verf\u00fcgung zu stellen, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "45.960", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "46.240", 
   "id": "s000017", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "sondern auch, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "46.240", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "51.480", 
   "id": "s000018", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "f\u00fcr die Entwicklung des gesamten Bildungssystems in den Partnerstaaten zu sorgen. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "51.480", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "53.160", 
   "id": "s000019", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Dazu geh\u00f6rt, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "53.160", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "57.600", 
   "id": "s000020", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "dass man Bildungsentwicklungspl\u00e4ne aufstellt und dass diese evaluiert werden. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "57.600", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "60.720", 
   "id": "s000021", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Dazu geh\u00f6ren auch der Schulbau und die Ausbildung von Lehrern. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "60.720", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "61.880", 
   "id": "s000022", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Insofern, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "61.880", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "63.040", 
   "id": "s000023", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Herr Klein, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "63.040", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "71.960", 
   "id": "s000024", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "ist die Globale Entwicklungspartnerschaft Voraussetzung f\u00fcr andere Formen der Zusammenarbeit im bildungspolitischen Bereich in Entwicklungsl\u00e4ndern. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "71.960", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "76.880", 
   "id": "s000025", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Deshalb m\u00fcssen wir uns noch einmal diesem Thema ganz besonders widmen und uns fragen: "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "76.880", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "80.480", 
   "id": "s000026", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Was kann die Bundesrepublik Deutschland in diesem Zusammenhang tun? "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "80.480", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "83.880", 
   "id": "s000027", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Ich will noch einmal deutlich machen\u00a0\u2013 "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "83.880", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "86.000", 
   "id": "s000028", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "deshalb ist das Thema so wichtig\u00a0\u2013: "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "86.000", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "88.880", 
   "id": "s000029", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Bildung ist der Schl\u00fcssel f\u00fcr Entwicklung. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "88.880", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "91.480", 
   "id": "s000030", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Das gilt f\u00fcr jeden einzelnen Menschen ganz genauso, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "91.480", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "93.800", 
   "id": "s000031", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "wie es f\u00fcr Staaten gilt; "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "93.800", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "96.640", 
   "id": "s000032", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "darauf haben meine Vorredner hingewiesen."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "96.640", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "102.680", 
   "id": "s000033", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Wenn man in den aktuellen Report der Vereinten Nationen schaut, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "102.680", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "105.040", 
   "id": "s000034", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "dann findet man eine Zahl, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "105.040", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "107.120", 
   "id": "s000035", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "die schon erschrecken muss: "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "107.120", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "112.800", 
   "id": "s000036", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "\u00dcber 260\u00a0Millionen\u00a0Kinder und Jugendliche haben keine M\u00f6glichkeit, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "112.800", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "114.120", 
   "id": "s000037", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "die Schule zu besuchen. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "114.120", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "118.040", 
   "id": "s000038", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "260\u00a0Millionen! "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "118.040", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "123.520", 
   "id": "s000039", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Das ist mehr als die H\u00e4lfte der gesamten Einwohnerschaft der Europ\u00e4ischen Union. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "123.520", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "124.680", 
   "id": "s000040", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Ich finde, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "124.680", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "128.200", 
   "id": "s000041", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "eine solche Zahl stellt wirklich eine Herausforderung dar, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "128.200", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "129.080", 
   "id": "s000042", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "dar\u00fcber nachzudenken, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "129.080", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "132.240", 
   "id": "s000043", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "ob wir in diesem Zusammenhang genug tun, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "132.240", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "137.000", 
   "id": "s000044", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "ob wir nicht mehr tun k\u00f6nnen und mehr tun m\u00fcssen."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "137.000", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "141.520", 
   "id": "s000045", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Seit gestern tagt die Geberkonferenz. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "141.520", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "143.640", 
   "id": "s000046", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Das Ziel, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "143.640", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "146.000", 
   "id": "s000047", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "das sich diese Konferenz vorgenommen hat, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "146.000", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "146.320", 
   "id": "s000048", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "ist, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "146.320", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "153.560", 
   "id": "s000049", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "3,1\u00a0Milliarden\u00a0Dollar f\u00fcr einen Bildungsfonds einzusammeln. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "153.560", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "156.160", 
   "id": "s000050", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Zur Wahrheit geh\u00f6rt, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "156.160", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "159.240", 
   "id": "s000051", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "dass die letzte Geberkonferenz ihr Ziel deutlich verfehlt hat; "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "159.240", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "162.160", 
   "id": "s000052", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "damals ging es um 3,5\u00a0Milliarden\u00a0Euro. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "162.160", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "165.560", 
   "id": "s000053", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "2,1\u00a0Milliarden\u00a0Euro sind damals zusammengekommen."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "165.560", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "171.680", 
   "id": "s000054", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Insofern m\u00fcssen wir dar\u00fcber reden, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "171.680", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "175.480", 
   "id": "s000055", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "ob auch Deutschland einen weiteren Beitrag leisten kann. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "175.480", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "179.560", 
   "id": "s000056", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Insofern spricht der Antrag der Gr\u00fcnen einen kritischen Punkt an."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "179.560", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "184.200", 
   "id": "s000057", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "In den letzten Jahren belief sich unser Beitrag auf 7\u00a0Millionen\u00a0Euro; "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "184.200", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "186.600", 
   "id": "s000058", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "diese Summe wurde genannt. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "186.600", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "194.440", 
   "id": "s000059", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Meine Kollegin Sonja Steffen hat in den Haushaltsberatungen mit daf\u00fcr gesorgt, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "194.440", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "197.960", 
   "id": "s000060", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "dass der Beitrag aufgestockt werden konnte."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "197.960", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "200.960", 
   "id": "s000061", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Ob das ein beachtlicher Betrag war, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "200.960", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "201.560", 
   "id": "s000062", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Herr Klein, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "201.560", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "203.360", 
   "id": "s000063", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "daran scheiden sich die Geister. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "203.360", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "205.040", 
   "id": "s000064", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "2\u00a0Millionen sind hinzugekommen, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "205.040", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "208.520", 
   "id": "s000065", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "jetzt sind es 9\u00a0Millionen\u00a0Euro pro Jahr. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "208.520", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "209.840", 
   "id": "s000066", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Ich finde, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "209.840", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "212.360", 
   "id": "s000067", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "da ist noch Luft nach oben, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "212.360", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "219.040", 
   "id": "s000068", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "und dar\u00fcber werden wir miteinander diskutieren m\u00fcssen."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "219.040", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "223.280", 
   "id": "s000069", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Die Erwartung des Sekretariats liegt bei 50\u00a0Millionen pro Jahr. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "223.280", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "224.960", 
   "id": "s000070", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Die Frage ist: "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "224.960", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "230.800", 
   "id": "s000071", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "K\u00f6nnen wir uns dieser Erwartung zumindest noch ein St\u00fcck weit n\u00e4hern?"
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "230.800", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "233.080", 
   "id": "s000072", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Ich will an dieser Stelle\u00a0\u2013 "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "233.080", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "235.200", 
   "id": "s000073", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "auch in Richtung der Gr\u00fcnenfraktion\u00a0\u2013 "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "235.200", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "236.600", 
   "id": "s000074", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "sagen: "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "236.600", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "237.520", 
   "id": "s000075", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Der Antrag geht so, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "237.520", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "238.600", 
   "id": "s000076", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "wie er gestellt ist, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "238.600", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "240.440", 
   "id": "s000077", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "in gewisser Weise ins Leere. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "240.440", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "245.960", 
   "id": "s000078", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Denn die Bundesregierung sitzt im Moment zwar dort am Verhandlungstisch\u00a0\u2013 "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "245.960", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "248.480", 
   "id": "s000079", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "wenn auch nur mit dem Botschafter\u00a0\u2013, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "248.480", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "252.960", 
   "id": "s000080", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "ist aber an die Haushaltsbeschl\u00fcsse gebunden. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "252.960", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "259.320", 
   "id": "s000081", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Sie kann also bei der Geberkonferenz nicht \u00fcber diese Haushaltsbeschl\u00fcsse hinausgehen."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "259.320", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "263.760", 
   "id": "s000082", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Es wird als Haushaltsgesetzgeber und Parlament unsere Aufgabe sein, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "263.760", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "266.800", 
   "id": "s000083", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "in den kommenden Haushaltsberatungen daf\u00fcr zu sorgen, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "266.800", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "277.080", 
   "id": "s000084", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "dass dieser Spielraum gr\u00f6\u00dfer wird und sich die Bundesrepublik Deutschland mit einem deutlich gr\u00f6\u00dferen Beitrag an der Globalen Entwicklungspartnerschaft beteiligt."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "277.080", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "278.680", 
   "id": "s000085", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Es w\u00e4re gut, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "278.680", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "286.000", 
   "id": "s000086", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "wenn wir Ihren Antrag heute in den Ausschuss \u00fcberweisen und dort gemeinsam besprechen, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "286.000", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "289.880", 
   "id": "s000087", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "mit welchen Positionen man in Haushaltsberatungen gehen kann, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "289.880", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "292.800", 
   "id": "s000088", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "die irgendwann dann hoffentlich kommen werden. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "292.800", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "295.320", 
   "id": "s000089", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Unser gemeinsames Ziel muss sein, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "295.320", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "298.080", 
   "id": "s000090", 
